(4. give a clear recommendation and screening disclaimer,) Tj
T*
(5. save assessments for later retrieval,) Tj
T*
(6. export PDF reports,) Tj
T*
(7. continue to function in limited form when the backend is offline,) Tj
T*
(8. provide quality-check and model-statistics views for transparency.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The current implementation follows a prioritized multimodal stack:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- text_transformer is the primary text scorer,) Tj
T*
(- audio is the primary audio scorer,) Tj
T*
(- image_dl is the primary image scorer,) Tj
T*
(- comorbidity blends classifier-chain output with upstream modality consensus.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Why This Matters) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The main value of the project is not only prediction accuracy. It is the complete workflow.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The system aims to:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- reduce friction for front-line screening,) Tj
T*
(- make the output understandable,) Tj
T*
(- preserve the record for follow-up,) Tj
T*
(- support language access,) Tj
T*
(- and keep the app useful even when the network is unreliable.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(That combination is especially relevant in rural or community settings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Proposed System Design) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Frontend) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The frontend is responsible for:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- language switching,) Tj
T*
(- profile and questionnaire entry,) Tj
T*
(- narrative input,) Tj
T*
(- optional media capture,) Tj
T*
(- adaptive test flow,) Tj
T*
(- preview rendering,) Tj
T*
(- result interpretation,) Tj
T*
(- records and reports browsing,) Tj
T*
(- record deletion,) Tj
T*
(- report hiding,) Tj
T*
(- offline status messaging.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
